      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered masterpiece. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. Power is managed by a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The exterior retains its factory depth with no swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster wear. The suspension has been refreshed with OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the razor-sharp turn-in and hydraulic steering feedback that defines this chassis. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning collector.",
